<abstract><t>In DMM scenario, it is possible for the MN to use multiple mobility anchor points and corresponding prefixes. In that case, MN needs to know the property of the addresses then it can select the optimized one for application to use. This document defines new IP network prefix types to assist address selection for applications.</t></abstract>

